        I Have just spent time in hospital with a Cardiac event - an arrhythmia
      </h2>
    
      <div class="body">
        I have just spent time in Cardio ward with an arrhythmia , I have been sent home with medication and follow up to determine cause. Can  I still get cover, what documentation is required from hospital/doctors in order for me to be covered. I booked my holiday last Thursday and was going to arrange travel insurance on the weekend. 
      </div>
    
